ActCanada Evidence Act
SubjectAuditor General of Canada - Access to information
PrecisOrder directing that AUDITOR GENERAL OF CANADA be granted access to the information that constitutes a confidence of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada, as defined in subsection 39(2) of the CANADA EVIDENCE ACT, that comes into existence on or after November 4, 2015, for the purposes of any Act of Parliament.
